## 4. Course objectives 🟢

- Introduce learners to the concepts and architecture of full-stack web development.
- Develop practical competence in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, JDBC, Servlets, JSP, and ReactJS.
- Enable students to design database-driven web applications using Java-based technologies.
- Build an understanding of Spring Boot fundamentals and enterprise application flow.
- Promote teamwork, documentation, and project demonstration through a mini full-stack capstone.

