## 8. 🔵 Differentiated instruction (mapped to the two levels)

**Reaching the floor (awareness level) — for students at risk of not clearing it:**
- Guided HTML/CSS/JavaScript starter templates and live walkthroughs.
- Stepwise lab sheets with checkpoints for JDBC/Servlet/JSP basics.
- Remedial mentoring on DOM manipulation, form validation, and session handling.

**Reaching the ceiling (advanced level) — for students aiming above 8 CGPA:**
- Optional extensions such as React component reuse, custom hooks, and Spring Boot service-layer design.
- Stretch tasks for clean architecture, validation, error handling, and project documentation.
- Capstone enhancement using role-based flows, secured endpoints, and polished UI design.

