## 22. Merrill strategy implementation audit 🔵

> The course uses a four-step learning cycle across the practical sessions: activation → demonstration → application → integration.

| Phase | Implementation evidence in this course |
|---|---|
| Activation | Introductory real-world examples, architecture overview, and recap-based discussions |
| Demonstration | Faculty walkthrough of HTML/CSS/JS, JDBC, React components, and Spring Boot basics |
| Application | Students complete guided practicals such as form validation, servlets, JSP integration, and React state tasks |
| Integration | Final mini-project combines frontend, backend, and database into a complete application |

